channel.title: Regarding the usage of Redash logo
channel.description: Our team has built app integrated with Redash APIs. It is still in Beta but will be released in a few month to the public. We would like to know if there is any process to use Redash logo(e.g: submit application etc) in our system, web site, sales documents?

item.title: Regarding the usage of Redash logo
item.dc:creator: arikfr
item.description:
Let’s follow up via email – I sent you an email about this just now (to the address in your profile).

Thanks.
